            <div class="article_head ">
                
                <h1>UK gov says new Home Sec <i>will</i> have powers to ban end-to-end encryption</h1>
                
                <h2>Amber Rudd yet to emerge from blanket of ministerial double-speak</h2>
                


                    <div class=img_caption>New UK Home Secretary Amber Rudd ... (Pic source: Department of Energy and Climate Change)</div>

                <div id=social_btns class="alt_colour dcl">
